<section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="row row-4-md p-big flex-even">
        <div class="col-6 col-5-md">
            <h2>Form Component</h2>
            <p>
                Robin restyles form elements to look clean, simple, and readable.
                At present the restyled elements are input, select, textarea, and 
                buttons (for buttons, see the next section).
                To apply the form stylings, do:
            </p>
            <pre><code>
&lt;form&gt;
    &lt;input class=&quot;input&quot;&gt;
    &lt;select class=&quot;select&quot;&gt;
        &lt;!-- Your select options here --&gt;
    &lt;/select&gt;
    &lt;textarea class=&quot;textarea&quot;&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;
&lt;/form&gt;
            </code></pre>
            <p>
                As with all components, form styles can be easily tweaked
                in <span class="code-quote">_variables.scss</span>. Be sure
                to check our <a href="/example">example page</a> to see how
                forms look.

            </p>
            

        </div>
    </div>
</section>
